PN,44801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FThere were "insufficient numbers" of
OL,7,Fpolice to clear the public from areas
OL,8,Fbeing searched for Noah Donohoe, the
OL,9,Finquest into his death has heard.
OL,11,FA retired PSNI officer said
OL,12,F"conspiracy theories" on social media
OL,13,Fencouraged people to gather in north
OL,14,FBelfast, and sections of the crowd
OL,15,Fwere "antagonistic" to police.
OL,17,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,18,Fschoolboy, which is being heard with a
OL,19,Fjury at Belfast Coroner's Court, is in
OL,20,Fits 11th week.
OL,26,@nD@LOUnD@aO]tD@AOUtD@UO]wD@FOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,7,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,8,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,9,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,10,Fleaving home on his bike to meet two
OL,11,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,15,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FRetired inspector Menary, who managed
OL,7,Fthe PSNI hazardous environment search
OL,8,F(HES) team, told jurors the unit was
OL,9,Fsent to the scene on June 23 to
OL,10,Fexamine the area surrounding the storm
OL,11,Fdrain.
OL,13,FMr Menary said his team was not
OL,14,Fdeployed to search the culvert until
OL,15,Fthe morning of June 24 because only
OL,16,Ftwo personnel were available,
OL,17,Fclarifying that this was a search and
OL,18,Fnot a rescue team.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FHe entered the culvert for around 40
OL,7,Fminutes, which he described as a "very
OL,8,Fhostile environment".
OL,10,FBrenda Campbell KC, representing
OL,11,FNoah's mother Fiona Donohoe, asked how
OL,12,Flong it would have taken for the
OL,13,Fteenager to travel through the tunnel
OL,14,Fnaked and in pitch darkness.
OL,16,FMr Menary said it "depends how
OL,17,Fdetermined you are to get through it"
OL,18,Fbut "probably less than an hour".
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@TO]xD@SOUyD@eO]zD@EOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FHe later expressed concerns over the
OL,7,Fpotential for toxic gases in the
OL,8,Fculvert, despite police logs from
OL,9,FSergeant Hutchings ` the lead police
OL,10,Fsearch adviser ` claiming there was no
OL,11,Fnoxious gas in the tunnel and it was
OL,12,Fsafe for search and rescue, and a
OL,13,Fstatement from the lead officer of the
OL,14,Fdive team who said it was "low risk".
OL,16,FMs Campbell read a statement from one
OL,17,Fof the diving specialist officers who
OL,18,Ffound Noah's body in the culvert on
OL,19,FJune 27, six days after he was last
OL,20,Fseen.
OL,26,@vD@[OUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FThe section of tunnel was 18ft long
OL,7,Fand 4ft in diameter, with around 1ft
OL,8,Fof silt across the bottom.
OL,10,FCounsel for Ms Donohoe put it to the
OL,11,Fretired officer: "As a search you have
OL,12,Ftaken from the Tuesday, the Wednesday,
OL,13,Fthe Thursday during office hours, a
OL,14,Fbit of the Friday, and it's not until
OL,15,Fthe Saturday that Noah's body was
OL,16,Fsadly found, and that's a journey that
OL,17,Fin your estimation a child could
OL,18,Fundertake in about an hour?"
OL,20,FMr Menary agreed.
OL,26,@sD@ROUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FAsked if he accepted his search was a
OL,7,Ffailure he said: "No. My search was
OL,8,Fthorough, it was safe, I regret we did
OL,9,Fnot find him on the evening of the
OL,10,FThursday and certainly on the Friday,
OL,11,Ffor it to go beyond that was a failure
OL,12,Fon my part."
OL,14,FThe former officer was questioned
OL,15,Fabout the crowds that gathered in
OL,16,FNorthwood Linear Park to help search
OL,17,Ffor Noah.
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FMs Campbell said people had gathered
OL,7,Fpartially due to "delay", adding that
OL,8,Fif the search "had started with a
OL,9,Fsense of urgency that got your team
OL,10,Fthere on the Tuesday", the crowd would
OL,11,Fnot have been there.
OL,13,FMr Menary said "there were quite a
OL,14,Fnumber of people that were
OL,15,Fantagonistic towards the team when
OL,16,Fthey arrived" but the majority were
OL,17,Fwell-intentioned.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@XO]pD@OOUrD@UO]uD@POUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,F"All sorts of stories and conspiracy
OL,7,Ftheories floating about on social
OL,8,Fmedia and some sections of the public
OL,9,Fwere being wound up by other members
OL,10,Fof the public, they were angry at the
OL,11,Fpolice, they were angry at anybody
OL,12,Fthere, so when the team got there they
OL,13,Fwere quite hostile," he said.
OL,15,FA police log was read which showed
OL,16,Fofficers at Linear Park "decided to
OL,17,Fsuspend the search and break for lunch
OL,18,Fin the hope that the crowd would
OL,19,Fdisperse or thin out".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]xD@YOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FMr Menary agreed that controlling the
OL,7,Fcrowd to conduct a search for a high-
OL,8,Frisk missing person is a "policing
OL,9,Fissue", but said there was a
OL,10,F"disruptive" element, adding "with a
OL,11,Fcrowd that size you'd need a number of
OL,12,Fpublic order units to clear the park".
OL,14,FA police log from the return after
OL,15,Flunch at 1pm describes "hundreds" of
OL,16,Fpeople still in Linear Park and an
OL,17,F"angry exchange and lots of shouting"
OL,18,Fbetween some members of the public and
OL,19,Fresidents of Northwood Road.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@FO]rD@AOUrD@LO]rD@^OUtD@eO]wD@
OL,26,AXOUwD@aO]yD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FA log from 1.20pm says the park had
OL,7,Fbeen cleared and the search was
OL,8,Fresumed.
OL,10,FMs Campbell asked why this was not
OL,11,Fdone in the morning, and Mr Menary
OL,12,Fsaid there was a "lack of police
OL,13,Fresources at the time to ensure there
OL,14,Fwas a sterile area for the search".
OL,16,FThe KC said: "There was insufficient
OL,17,Fpolice numbers there to let you get on
OL,18,Fwith your job of searching for a high-
OL,19,Frisk missing child?"
OL,21,FMr Menary replied: "Yes that's right."
OL,26,@tD@ROUvD@bO]xD@NOU{D@TO]}D@TOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FThe inquest previously heard that a
OL,7,FCCTV camera in the back garden of a
OL,8,Fhouse in Northwood Road would have
OL,9,Fcaptured footage of the area around
OL,10,Fthe entrance to the storm drain but it
OL,11,Fwas never viewed by police.
OL,13,FMs Campbell asked Mr Menary how
OL,14,Fdifferent his search would have been
OL,15,Fif Noah had been seen in that area.
OL,17,FHe agreed that if there had been
OL,18,Fevidence of Noah entering the culvert
OL,19,F"the search strategy would have been
OL,20,Fdifferent".
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,F"If Noah had been seen going into the
OL,7,Ftunnel and not going out it would have
OL,8,Fbeen a rescue situation," he said.
OL,10,FThe former officer earlier confirmed
OL,11,Fhe was aware on the evening of June 23
OL,12,Fthat the culvert was tidal and would
OL,13,Fbe flooded with water at regular
OL,14,Fintervals.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,FThe court was shown transcripts of
OL,7,Fevidence to the inquest from Sergeant
OL,8,FHutchings ` the lead police search
OL,9,Fadviser ` which said he was made aware
OL,10,Fthe culvert was tidal on June 26 and
OL,11,Fsubsequently "changed tack" to deploy
OL,12,Fdivers.
OL,14,FMr Menary said he had made another
OL,15,Fsearch adviser on duty at the time
OL,16,Faware that the culvert was tidal,
OL,17,Fleading Ms Campbell to ask if he was
OL,18,Fconcerned about a "breakdown of
OL,19,Fcommunication" between the advisers.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@[O]zD@SOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776431470
OL,3,C'Insufficient' police numbers to clear
OL,4,Ccrowds for Noah Donohoe search
OL,6,F"It concerns me it wasn't part of the
OL,7,Fflow of information but the search
OL,8,Fprobably wouldn't have changed its
OL,9,Fcourse of action it was going on," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
